Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.76,0:00:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今 我到底還能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了改變那如狹隘庭園般的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.15,0:00:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還活不到人生的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反抗 相擁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在無意識中被刻上的經驗紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當站在懸崖邊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苦難抓住了我的手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.38,0:00:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次看到了自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.38,0:00:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往更加寬廣的領域\N往更深更大的某處
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.49,0:01:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝著無法預測的世界前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.43,0:01:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And lt's calling me again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.47,0:01:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,12月的平均氣溫為23度？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.35,0:01:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以游泳了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.44,0:01:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次旅遊會很有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼會允許那個人做獨家採訪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.36,0:01:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後和自衛隊的聯合作戰任務會增加
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.57,0:01:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的秘密武器遲早也會曝光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.37,0:01:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再者，口頭上的敷衍還是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:01:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.54,0:02:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.25,0:02:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿！能來這個南方小島我很高興，不過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.25,0:02:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於實地的採訪…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.05,0:02:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會派一位很可愛的人做你的嚮導
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.47,0:02:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太期待了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢！看到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇，那就是人類的堡壘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對MU作戰的最前線
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.35,0:02:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根來彼方島
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.37,0:02:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是一個抽像藝術品？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.16,0:02:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是從奈裡亞神殿遺跡中運回來的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你違反了守密原則
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.88,0:02:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡都是相關人員
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.96,0:02:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來要做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擔心？我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼，來試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.16,0:03:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許如月博士知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.75,0:03:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.75,0:03:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人好像什麼都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不清楚它的構造是怎樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.85,0:04:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然她不在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.86,0:04:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑道和機庫均已清理至4級
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有硬件方面的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:36.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與無人戰機的協作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和地球聯合使用的程序\N我們差不多都可以適應了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最大的問題在於維護保養部門
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對他們不滿意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.87,0:04:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們的技術的確不錯，但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.17,0:04:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無人戰機沒有靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.17,0:04:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靈魂啊命運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.88,0:04:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出生在20世紀的人就喜歡那樣虛幻的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白人的壞毛病就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.84,0:04:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只相信能看見的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:04:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想讓我在客廳裡放些黃色的東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們兩年來的第一次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可你們都一點沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？真是有兩年沒見了呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你邀我來這個小隊，bunga mawar
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:21.45,*note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}bunga mawar：印尼語，薔薇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是艾爾菲·哈迪亞特中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天開始，被任命為TERRA空軍Alpha小隊隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說了，祝你好運，中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾爾菲·哈迪亞特中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊，是那個唯一從Overlord行動中\N生還的飛行員吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸運女神？不，或者是死神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:05:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個美人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tokyo Jupiter裡面怎麼樣啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東京塔真的是藍的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時間的話我一定要聽聽你的經歷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去過管理部了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.46,0:06:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們讓你到任後就去那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.18,0:06:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.97,0:06:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威風凜凜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打賭她是個「女神」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:33.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不喜歡賭博
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.36,0:06:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.57,0:06:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把現場的事情都扔給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.44,0:06:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是你的，從本州帶來的紀念品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊，多謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡甜食
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有，我想讓你給別人當一回嚮導
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚮導？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此，他就是那個「可愛的人」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是天戶通訊的貳神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們允許我對TERRA進行採訪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼帶他在人工島轉轉就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.34,0:07:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩了，如果可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢！五味君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.35,0:07:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些是從本州帶的紀念品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點都沒變啊，亙理先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.07,0:07:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有輕微的震動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.28,0:07:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近來他挺合作嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獨自離開了故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.16,0:07:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個為拯救世界而戰的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諷刺的語氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.58,0:07:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你誤會了，我真是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.67,0:07:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能進來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是，請進
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把衣服放在那裡就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，再見…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七森小姐，你和遙關係很好，是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:07:58.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊，但我們還算不上摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:08:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遙喜歡什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.57,0:08:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她喜歡喝酒，我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是為聖誕節準備嗎？\N不問小惠的愛好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為她比較容易瞭解…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡和東京的差別並沒有那麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和家人分開後，不孤單嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真覺得痛苦，也沒必要強忍著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.17,0:08:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊，你今天要調到戰術部去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.48,0:08:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾人君嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.06,0:08:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他做的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.94,0:08:41.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說在分析部門進行實驗時很合作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已經適應了島上的生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.07,0:08:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意外的，他很堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,0:08:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道他是不是遇上了好人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？這是八雲君的經驗麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總一，那個記者怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個，處理了一些事情後就立刻去採訪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去本島了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.46,0:08:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到根來島？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:09:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為要留在這裡一陣子\N他說要去找一個以後可以常去的商店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人到這裡來幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是聯合軍的監察官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.64,0:09:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來監視你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.48,0:09:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不記得了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們半夜一起偷跑出去…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你來找我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是以失敗告終
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那些人中間你不感覺內心空虛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，我一直都是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說這種冷漠無情的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.05,0:09:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是冷漠無情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.77,0:09:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我拿一瓶了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.65,0:10:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.07,0:10:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個，那樣是喝不到的，因為有個小球堵著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.16,0:10:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得把它轉到凹槽裡面去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您在度假嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.67,0:10:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,單身赴任
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工薪族很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說這個你能明白嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.47,0:10:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以多少我還能理解一點的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.76,0:10:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失敬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.97,0:10:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？那個…我開車，之後把比薩餅…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送比薩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:39.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還有這種活啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「D-1出現，馬上返回」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.07,0:10:46.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要工作了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.07,0:10:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊，再會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個空瓶子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方便的話，退給商店可以拿到退瓶費
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.54,0:11:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在太平洋上確認的D-1全高為6000米
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它正以40公里的時速向根來彼方島前進
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,預計作戰時間為1408
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.26,0:11:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1408是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.47,0:11:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊，那個\N那個是指14點08分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.47,0:11:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據現在大約20分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.47,0:12:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標D-1很可能為兩足步行型
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據推測腿和生長出來的部分長度約為5千米
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.77,0:12:08.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左右兩邊的形狀應該是完全相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？為什麼只有腿說明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.86,0:12:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.45,0:12:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只能看到腿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是這房子的主人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以打擾你一會兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.68,0:12:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發現目標
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從11點到13點方向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距離10000
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.64,0:12:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D-1影像確認，在12點方向，情況確認
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各機維持隊形接近目標
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,RahXephon在後方待機
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解！瞭解！瞭解！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要為我同伴的死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.16,0:12:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,復仇！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.26,0:13:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擊中了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過，還沒結束
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它不是站著的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是飄浮著的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被外形誤導了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.94,0:13:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Alpha和Bravo，在16點方向散開！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.77,0:13:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Blue隊形
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.37,0:13:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風水不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一個人住？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名牌上有三個不同的姓氏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.47,0:14:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是親戚嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個侄女和一個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾牌？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能依靠孩子的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.06,0:14:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全國小學生繪畫比賽…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2009年的參加者名單裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.06,0:14:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有神名綾人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:15:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候他五年級…\N如果現在還活著的話就有29歲了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我這裡的綾人只有17歲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說，另有其人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D-1詠歎調
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:31.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.06,0:15:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退！讓Alpha-1隊撤回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.57,0:15:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Alpha-1隊沒有回音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不要再…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.55,0:16:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,RahXephon正在放出量子波
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在歌唱？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.35,0:16:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧，艾爾菲小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.15,0:16:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別管我，注意敵人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.36,0:16:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.96,0:16:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾人君！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心，只要他在座艙裡就不會被電擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.34,0:16:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問題是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.44,0:17:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,RahXephon活動停止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機師的生命維持降低至3級！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾人君，請回答！綾人君！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾人君！綾人君！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾人君！聽到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請快回答
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.67,0:17:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快，不做點什麼的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.85,0:17:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以動嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾人君！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差一點…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就差一點…！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滾開！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.77,0:18:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滾開！滾開！滾開！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滾開！滾開！滾開！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.06,0:19:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tokyo…Jupiter？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.65,0:19:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.15,0:19:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,響亮的音色…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不存在於戰爭之火中…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你錯了，olin
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再來一局如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.04,0:19:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有機會我會再來拜訪的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六道博士…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,單機突入不明雲層！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自作主張是違反軍紀的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種戰鬥方式是會讓你送命的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.47,0:19:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我自己的命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.85,0:19:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你！你是認真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.14,0:19:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.85,0:19:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要單機突入
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為指揮官，我按最佳方式進行了判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.65,0:19:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.94,0:19:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.94,0:19:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.15,0:19:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你是違反了軍紀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁閉兩天，就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.58,0:19:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.17,0:20:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣如何，監察官先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.35,0:20:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不覺得我們很無恥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓一個被綁架來的孩子為我們作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.07,0:20:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想，這次該輪到我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.16,0:20:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後還請照顧他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.75,0:20:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我不能上戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您一直在這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.06,0:21:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很舒服的風，不知不覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.27,0:21:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吹吹風，可以使人心情舒暢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.37,0:21:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼要工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.16,0:21:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為家境問題？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.96,0:21:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.67,0:21:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.25,0:21:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東京在哪個方向…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是感覺它們之間有某種聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.64,0:21:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.24,0:23:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遙遠的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.24,0:23:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聳立的純白冰樹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.16,0:23:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱著黑暗心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.37,0:23:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,RahXephon第八樂章
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.66,0:23:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰封聖誕夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.17,0:23:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個世界飽含著聲音
